# End-to-End Sales Data Analysis (Capstone Project)

This project performs an end-to-end data analysis on a retail sales dataset.

## Objectives
- Clean and explore the dataset
- Calculate key performance metrics
- Perform exploratory data analysis
- Visualize insights using charts

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Key Insights
- Identified top performing sub-categories by sales
- Analyzed distribution of sales values
- Explored relationships between sales, profit, quantity and discount

## Visualizations
- Sales by Sub-Category
- Top Sub-Categories by Sales
- Sales Distribution
- Correlation Heatmap

